"title": "4854: weather, God's sovereignty over",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4854: weather, god's sovereignty over",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The weather is under the control of God, who alone is able to direct it.</p>\n<h2>The weather is under God's control</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:25-Job28:27\">JOB 28:25–28:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:26–8:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:39–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:10\">JOB 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:8-Job26:9\">JOB 26:8–26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:13\">JOB 26:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:1-Job37:18\">JOB 37:1–37:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:16-Ps147:18\">PSA 147:16–147:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:8\">PSA 148:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a></p>\n<h2>God alone understands the mysteries of the weather</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:19-Prov3:20\">PRO 3:19–3:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:8\">JHN 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:26-Job36:33\">JOB 36:26–36:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22-Job38:30\">JOB 38:22–38:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:34-Job38:35\">JOB 38:34–38:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:37\">JOB 38:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:3-Eccl11:5\">ECC 11:3–11:5</a></p>\n<h2>Israel's economy was dependent on the weather</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:4\">LEV 26:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:10-Deut11:15\">DEU 11:10–11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:24\">JER 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:3\">HOS 6:3</a></p>\n<h2>The weather demonstrates God's goodness and mercy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:14-Gen9:16\">GEN 9:14–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:13-Deut33:14\">DEU 33:13–33:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:7-Ps68:9\">PSA 68:7–68:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:23\">ISA 30:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:23\">JOL 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:1\">ZEC 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>The weather as a demonstration of God's direct intervention</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:4\">JON 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:21\">EXO 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:31\">NUM 11:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:26\">PSA 78:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8\">JON 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>The weather as an answer to prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:17-1Sam12:18\">1SA 12:17–12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:35-1Kgs8:36\">1KI 8:35–8:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:41-1Kgs18:44\">1KI 18:41–18:44</a></p>\n<h2>The weather can cause suffering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:40\">GEN 31:40</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:2\">ACT 28:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:9\">EZR 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:16\">JOB 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:18-Job1:19\">JOB 1:18–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:12\">MAT 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:18\">JHN 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:15\">ACT 27:15</a></p>",
